task.summary: Add resources to the project. Added collecting dependencies and building a zip kit.
Add 'AUTO' option to the <broadcast> setting, try and determine the broadcast mask automatically. Reset version to '1.0.0'.
Fixed NPE in NTProtocolHandler.procCloseFile(), context may be null. Change received packet debug to use the DBG_PKTTYPE debug level.
Changed default broadcast mask setting to 'AUTO', default dialects to 'SMB1'. Runsrv uses the new jfileserver-run.jar to launch the file server.
Changed jar build phase to use multiple executions to generate the main, Alfresco embedded and kit jar files.
Switch off debug in the notify change handler.
Add a default shared folder with a single test file to the default configuration.
Set a manifest for the default jfileserver.jar so that it is executable, expecting dependent libraries in a lib/ folder.
Fix Javadoc comments, added Javadoc to the pom.
